{
  "stem": "21349.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew already 1933 they had certain concentration camps, because we had a non-Jewish friend who was a doll doctor, he fixed dolls.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he-- but I don't know if he was a Communist or not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But anyhow, he was sent to concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know which the first one was, if it was Dachau or it was the other one, Buchenwald, one of these was the first.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sachsenhausen was formed in 1936, when they had the Olympics.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one day, his wife gets an urn with ashes in and said, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he was shot while he tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These are his ashes, already 1933.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I knew that there were some.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also from other people I heard at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They kept it all very quiet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I knew already at that time there were concentration camps and there were prisons and they were shooting and killing already at that time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When you left Germany-- when did you actually leave Germany?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We left Germany on March-- on May 31st, 1939.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on that day, we went from Bremen to Hamburg by train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we saw our relatives for the last time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we took a taxi from our relatives to the harbor, to the port.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at that time, we took a taxi.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the taxi had to make a detour.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I found out that the detour was because Goering, who was one of the Nazi officials, gave a talk.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was the first time where he talked openly, telling the German people that we are sending soldiers to Franco's Spain.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We knew this all the time, but he never wanted to acknowledge it.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
